Class Sign

  • java.lang.Object
    • game.model.GameObject
      • game.model.objects.WorldObject
        • game.model.objects.Sign
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BuildingSign

    public class Sign
extends WorldObject
    A road sign, represents a road crossing. The game's road system is build by joined signs.
